snippet.title: Shadows Peak (Early Access Trailer)
snippet.description:
Shadows Peak on steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/359940/

Shadows Peak is a story-driven atmospheric horror game focused on exploration. You play as a writer who decided to visit mysterious place called Shadows Peak to gather materials for a new book about legends. Be warned, Shadows Peak will not hold your hand.

http://vintsevych.com/
